          <h2>Kompetisi FIKSI 2026</h2>
          <p>
            Diajukan sebagai karya unggulan Teknologi Informasi dan Komunikasi
            tingkat nasional — firmware, PCB, dan web dashboard terintegrasi.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="comp-badges">
          <div class="comp-badge">
            <div class="comp-badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏆</div>
            <div>
              <div class="comp-badge-name">FIKSI 2026</div>
              <div class="comp-badge-sub">Festival Inovasi & Kreativitas Siswa</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-badge">
            <div class="comp-badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏫</div>
            <div>
              <div class="comp-badge-name">SMKN 1 Madiun</div>
              <div class="comp-badge-sub">Jawa Timur, Indonesia</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-badge">
            <div class="comp-badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</div>
            <div>
              <div class="comp-badge-name">IoT Hardware</div>
              <div class="comp-badge-sub">Firmware · PCB · Dashboard</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- ── ABOUT ── -->
    <section class="about-section" id="tentang" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">

        <div class="section-tag">Tentang Proyek</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="about-heading">Apa Itu OpenRelay?</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          Sistem kontroler relay IoT open source yang dibangun di atas ESP32,
          dirancang untuk memudahkan otomasi rumah dan industri dengan antarmuka modern.
        </p>

        <div class="about-grid reveal">

          <!-- Left: text -->
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              <strong>OpenRelay</strong> adalah proyek firmware, PCB, dan web dashboard
              terintegrasi untuk mengontrol relay secara lokal maupun jarak jauh
              melalui protokol MQTT.
            </p>
            <p>
              Dibuat sebagai proyek <strong>standalone</strong> — bukan WLED usermod —
              untuk kompetisi FIKSI 2026. OpenRelay mengadopsi identitas WLED
              sehingga kompatibel dengan ekosistem yang sudah ada.
            </p>
            <p>
              Sistem mendukung ekspansi GPIO menggunakan IC <strong>PCF8574</strong>
              dan <strong>MCP23017</strong>, memungkinkan hingga 128 relay dari satu
              unit ESP32 tanpa hardware tambahan yang mahal.
            </p>
            <p>
              Semua konfigurasi disimpan di <strong>LittleFS</strong> dan relay dapat
              dikontrol via MQTT, WebSocket lokal, maupun REST API bawaan.
            </p>

            <div class="about-highlights">
              <div class="highlight-item">Firmware ~1585 baris, 15 bug telah diperbaiki</div>
              <div class="highlight-item">PCB custom dirancang dengan EasyEDA</div>
              <div class="highlight-item">Dashboard web di GitHub Pages (HTTPS + MQTT WSS)</div>
              <div class="highlight-item">Watchdog hardware 10 detik untuk failsafe</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: spec card -->
          <div class="spec-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="spec-card-header">
              <div class="spec-card-title">// Spesifikasi Utama</div>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-rows">
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Platform</span>
                <span class="spec-val">ESP32 (espressif32)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Framework</span>
                <span class="spec-val">Arduino + PlatformIO</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Storage</span>
                <span class="spec-val">LittleFS 8MB</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Max Relay</span>
                <span class="spec-val">128 Channel</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Expander</span>
                <span class="spec-val">PCF8574 + MCP23017</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">MQTT Buffer</span>
                <span class="spec-val">2048 bytes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Watchdog</span>
                <span class="spec-val">10 detik (HW)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">OTA Update</span>
                <span class="spec-val">Supported</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">WLED Compat.</span>
                <span class="spec-val">v0.14.0-relay</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec-row">
                <span class="spec-key">Active Low</span>
                <span class="spec-val">Default (true)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div style="margin-top: 56px; display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;" class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="#features" class="btn btn-primary">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            </svg>
            Lihat Semua Fitur
          </a>
          <a href="#architecture" class="btn btn-outline">
            Baca Dokumentasi
          </a>
          <a href="#team" class="btn btn-ghost">
            Kenali Tim
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── FEATURES ── -->
    <section class="features-section" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">

        <div class="section-tag">Fitur Unggulan</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="features-heading">Semua yang Kamu Butuhkan</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          OpenRelay hadir dengan fitur lengkap dari firmware hingga dashboard, semua dalam satu paket open source.
        </p>

        <div class="features-grid reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
            <div class="feature-title">128 Relay Channel</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Ekspansi tak terbatas menggunakan PCF8574 dan MCP23017 melalui I2C. Satu ESP32 untuk semua kebutuhan.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
            <div class="feature-title">MQTT Native</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Kontrol relay dari mana saja via MQTT broker publik atau privat. Dukungan WSS untuk dashboard GitHub Pages.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
            <div class="feature-title">Web Dashboard</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Dashboard responsif berbasis GitHub Pages dengan HTTPS + MQTT WSS. Akses dari browser tanpa instalasi apapun.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔧</div>
            <div class="feature-title">PCB Custom</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Desain PCB menggunakan EasyEDA dengan dukungan I2S audio (INMP441), power management, dan ekspander GPIO.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-5">
            <div class="feature-icon">💾</div>
            <div class="feature-title">Konfigurasi Persisten</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Semua pengaturan (relay, sensor, config) tersimpan di LittleFS dan bertahan setelah restart atau update firmware.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-6">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
            <div class="feature-title">OTA Update</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Update firmware via jaringan WiFi tanpa perlu kabel. Password OTA dapat dikonfigurasi untuk keamanan.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-7">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔌</div>
            <div class="feature-title">Pattern Sequencer</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Buat urutan nyala/mati relay dengan timing kustom. Cocok untuk efek lampu, otomasi pabrik, dan demonstrasi.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-8">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <div class="feature-title">Sensor Digital</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Baca status sensor digital dan kirim ke MQTT secara real-time. Integrasi langsung dengan relay untuk otomasi.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-delay-9">
            <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
            <div class="feature-title">Watchdog & Failsafe</div>
            <div class="feature-description">
              Hardware watchdog 10 detik dan allOff() single-batch untuk keamanan. Relay tidak terjebak dalam kondisi ON saat crash.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── ARCHITECTURE ── -->
    <section class="architecture-section" id="architecture" aria-labelledby="architecture-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">

        <div class="section-tag">Arsitektur Sistem</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="architecture-heading">Bagaimana Cara Kerjanya</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          Tiga layer yang terpisah namun terintegrasi: hardware, firmware, dan web dashboard.
        </p>

        <div class="architecture-content reveal">
          <div class="arch-flow">
            <div class="arch-node">
              <div class="arch-node-icon">🌐</div>
              <div class="arch-node-title">Dashboard</div>
              <div class="arch-node-subtitle">GitHub Pages / Browser</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node">
              <div class="arch-node-icon">📡</div>
              <div class="arch-node-title">MQTT Broker</div>
              <div class="arch-node-subtitle">HiveMQ WSS :8884</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node">
              <div class="arch-node-icon">🔲</div>
              <div class="arch-node-title">ESP32</div>
              <div class="arch-node-subtitle">Firmware + LittleFS</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node">
              <div class="arch-node-icon">🔌</div>
              <div class="arch-node-title">Expander</div>
              <div class="arch-node-subtitle">PCF8574 / MCP23017</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node">
              <div class="arch-node-icon">⚡</div>
              <div class="arch-node-title">Relay</div>
              <div class="arch-node-subtitle">128 Channel</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="arch-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Pin Configuration</span>
              <span class="detail-value">SDA: IO21, SCL: IO22</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Interrupt (MCP23017)</span>
              <span class="detail-value">INTA: IO32, INTB: IO33</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Status LEDs</span>
              <span class="detail-value">IO16, IO17, IO25, IO26</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">I2S Microphone</span>
              <span class="detail-value">SCK: IO23, WS: IO14, SD: IO13</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Active Low Configuration</span>
              <span class="detail-value">true (default)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Maximum Relays</span>
              <span class="detail-value">128 channels</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── TEAM ── -->
    <section class="team-section" id="team" aria-labelledby="team-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">

        <div class="section-tag">Tim Pengembang</div>
